## TOOL CATEGORIES

Nibble Learn organizes 80+ tools into 6 main categories:

### 1. PLANNING & INSTRUCTION (~25 tools)
Focus: Lesson planning, curriculum development, instructional design

### 2. ASSESSMENT & FEEDBACK (~15 tools)
Focus: Creating assessments, grading, providing feedback

### 3. STUDENT SUPPORT (~12 tools)
Focus: Differentiation, IEPs, accommodation, intervention

### 4. COMMUNICATION (~10 tools)
Focus: Parent emails, newsletters, letters of recommendation

### 5. PRODUCTIVITY (~10 tools)
Focus: Text tools, translation, summarization, rewriting

### 6. COMMUNITY & ENGAGEMENT (~8 tools)
Focus: Team building, class culture, engagement activities

